;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 17:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/six-years-ago-fiona-apple-released-diy-grammy-winning-album-featuring-a-dead-dogs-bones-as-an-instrument/</guid></item></channel></rss>